    "description": "Byte The Dust 是一款精密的平台跳跃游戏，设定在一个庞大的关卡中，哪怕是最细微的失误，也会让玩家回到起点。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190620/extras/cb87f5bf18525ddd1c75ed5d4ed7cd24.avif?t=1755208855\" width=462 height=174 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作简单，挑战十足</h2>你只需要奔跑和跳跃，就这么简单！尽管操作方式很简单，但不要被迷惑，这些精心设计的关卡肯定会给你带来真正的挑战！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190620/extras/9f619e791647bc8d0f66d1aa7da87c47.apng?t=1755208855\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190620/extras/9f619e791647bc8d0f66d1aa7da87c47.poster.avif?t=1755208855\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小心惩罚管道</h2>如果你不小心跳跃失败，你可能会掉进惩罚管道。这是通向起点的单程之旅。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190620/extras/14144d8f796d17a98f3df1688b647fee.poster.avif?t=1755208855\" width=750 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190620/extras/14144d8f796d17a98f3df1688b647fee.webm?t=1755208855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190620/extras/14144d8f796d17a98f3df1688b647fee.mp4?t=1755208855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
